title: Quiche's  |  Life Saving Leftovers
description:
Learn the base + 4 Gorgeous Quiche's Inspirations ! Italian with cherry tomatoes and cured ham, Greek with Feta, Zucchini and mint, and discover the others in the video...

This video is part of a new series : Life Saving Leftovers. A waterfall of tips to make you a better cook with whatever there's in the fridge. Yes you can !

The complete recipe can be found here : 
http://www.frenchguycooking.com/wtf/171/quichess-life-saving-leftovers
